  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced working capital volatility, protected revenue, and sustained COGS/EBITDA during disruptions.]
  N4 -->|High-impact event detected| B1[Develop rapid response protocols and reallocate resources.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Protect revenue and working capital through proactive measures.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Geopolitical risk identified| B2[Adjust planning decisions to incorporate geopolitical risks.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Mitigate geopolitical risks affecting working capital and cost structure.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Insufficient data for accurate simula...| B3[Request additional data inputs and re-run simulations.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Ensure robust contingency plans based on comprehensive data.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]